reviews.text: Nice food, good Service, a young lady help us to order as we are 2 only and wanna a light food.
Tasty food and really good shisha with free coal change. They use good tobacco and coconut coal. Of course you should choose more expensive shisha option
Somewhere to chill out with friends

Shisha was good, one young staff with glasses is very rude no manners to speak she banged the light that they put under the shisha throwing it and she broke it. The food and shisha got too late to arrive so I just simply asked her how much time should we wait cuz we was starving to death she answered back with no politeness(atleast if u got manners to answer back). Never gonna recommend this place to my friends again.
Great place!
